[HostMyBytes](http://hostmybytes.com/) announces the latest data center location: Jacksonville, Florida, USA (GoRack).

While other cheap VPS companies are leaving Jacksonville (and the hosting industry) HostMyBytes is growing.  We are growing in the same data center (GoRack) with the same network that people **love** in Jacksonville.

Now welcoming all former Crissic Solutions customers!  Get migrated in Jacksonville before they have you offline.

![](http://hostmybytes.com/images/dont-like-the-ship-scaled.gif)
_Quadranet Creates Crissic VPS Refugees_

Initially, we are offering OpenVZ services only.  We have a [waiting list for KVM](https://docs.google.com/a/tplack.com/forms/d/1r4Al8gHB3nmYZrWbKBW79tXOPjMP3_0wiMrk67bVymU/viewform?usp=send_form) and inventory will become available as the list builds.

**Price Matching**&lt;br /&gt;

We will match all legitimate prices and plan specs for FORMER Crissic VPS customers (both on OpenVZ and KVM) who pay monthly.  Provide us with proof of recent cancellation (August 10th, 2015 or later) and proof of your plan pricing and plan spec. You can do that via [our ticketing system](http://clients.hostmybytes.com/submitticket.php).

